room_title: Escape room "Psycho Dentist" by The House of Clues in Santa Barbara
room_address: 629 N Salsipuedes St Santa Barbara, CA 93103
room_description: Dr. Zubovski is a psycho dentist - none of his patients have returned home from their appointments. No one knows what he looks like and where he operates, so it's been impossible to catch him. He is known for underground operations, kidnapping and organ trafficking. Beware!
